title: A touch of Frost. Complete, all 40 episodes (1992-2010), Dutch s
description:
A touch of Frost. Complete, all 40 episodes (1992-2010), Dutch subs


AVC x264 MKV, with integrated (not hardcoded) Dutch VobSubs, taken right of the DVD.

First 26 episodes are 4:3 aspect ratio, from series 8 on they are 16:9.
Encoded with Handbrake, contstant quality (RF20), Audio AAC Stereo.
Subs are VobSub, wich means, its a bitmap image, this can look soft/fuzzy when upscaled.

Enjoy and keep seeding this huge one!
